      "text": "end_session() Flow:\n1. Compress conversation → MID-tier\n2. Extract entities from compressed facts\n3. Process LLM extractions\n4. Store raw conversation log\n5. Run graph inference (transitive closure)\n6. Age all memories\n7. Suppress stale (10+ sessions)\n8. Delete old suppressed (30+ sessions)",
